fn.p: The percentage values are means of two determinations (two preparations of essential oil dilution in n-hexane), with relative standard deviation values (RSD%) below 20% for all components. a Linear retention index (LRI), experimentally obtained on a HP-5MS column using a C 7-C 30 mixture of n-alkanes. b Other abbreviations: n. = number assigned to compound, HM = Monoterpene Hydrocarbons; OM = oxygenated monoterpenes; HS = sesquiterpene Hydrocarbons; OS = Oxygenated Sesquiterpenes; PP = Phenyl Propanoids.
